The paper focuses on the development of tools and datasets for automated and precise identification of architecture and endianness of binary files and object code. This involves techniques related to reverse engineering, software behavior analysis, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.PL (Programming Languages), cs.AR (Architecture), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
